    KNNHeap<D>

    public class DistanceDBIDPairKNNHeap<D extends Distance<D>>
extends AbstractKNNHeap<DistanceDBIDPair<D>,D>
    Heap for collecting kNN candidates with arbitrary distance types. For double distances, see DoubleDistanceDBIDPairKNNHeap To instantiate, use DBIDUtil.newHeap(D, int) instead!
